{"id":3355,"date":"2023-03-14T17:41:04","date_gmt":"2023-03-14T16:41:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=3355"},"modified":"2023-03-15T11:40:42","modified_gmt":"2023-03-15T10:40:42","slug":"triple-training-toolkit","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/project-deliverables\/triple-training-toolkit\/","title":{"rendered":"TRIPLE Training Toolkit"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-center has-white-background-color has-background\">The TRIPLE Training Toolkit is an open workflow in five steps that trainers can reproduce and adapt to organise training events following a FAIR-by-design method. <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-white-background-color has-background\" style=\"font-size:16px\">It was created following the delivery of the <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/triple-open-science-training-series\/\">TRIPLE Open Science Training Series<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignfull size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"771\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12-1024x771.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3393\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12-1024x771.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12-300x226.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12-768x578.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12-1536x1157.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Capture-decran-2023-03-14-a-15.42.12.png 1856w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">This figure illustrates the TRIPLE Training Toolkit as a workflow in five steps with the aim to support trainers in organising FAIR-by-design training events and sharing the related training materials as Open Educational Resources (OERs). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">Starting from the center of the circle <em>&#8220;I want to&#8221;<\/em>, users are directed towards a phase of the workflow. For each phase of the process, specific template documents are indicated for trainers to reuse and adapt. Please note that the phases may overlap, they are not necessarily in chronological order.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-5 wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-luminous-vivid-amber-background-color has-background\" style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Start using the TRIPLE Training Toolkit<br><\/strong>The purpose of each template document according to the task you wish to carry out is explained below. <br>Click on the title of the files to download them. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator alignwide has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-3 wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<h3 class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#fad35c\"><strong>1. Design the series<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-dbfda2e0-a2ca-4eaf-aa6e-8d18622afe3b\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Internal_Training_Needs_Survey_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.docx\"><strong>Survey &#8211; Needs<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The methodology of the survey can be reproduced and shared with your community to better understand its needs and expectations in terms of training.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-09f710ab-1fad-41be-b466-0d5afcf2db84\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Training_Objectives_Learning_Outcomes_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.docx\"><strong>Learning objectives and learning outcomes <\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">This file serves as an example to show how clear objectives have been developed by the trainer and learning outcomes are identifiable by the trainee. The use of strong verbs focuses the attention of participants on what they will gain after having taken part in the training.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<h3 class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#f3a03d\"><strong>2. Organise the event<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-78775f3c-edb9-4370-a0db-04442d6c0fd0\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Guidelines_Organisation_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.docx\"><strong>Guidelines to organise training events<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">These step-by-step guidelines follow a FAIR by-design method to support organisers, speakers and moderators in the organisational aspects of the training. They help ensure your training events and resources are FAIR (findable, accessible, interoperable and reusable).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-9371adca-ae07-450b-910e-fbf6ff7e6d1a\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/To_Do_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.xlsx\"><strong>To-Do List<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">This template spreadsheet works as a planning of the activities. It helps organisers, moderators and speakers share the tasks related to the training event in a timely manner. It can be replicated for each training session to ensure the process is implemented consistently throughout the training series.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-8 wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<h3 class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#d28a96\"><strong>3. Promote and disseminate<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-56248d0b-ea4e-45ce-8c98-94d30d637442\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Enlarged_Audience_Template_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.xlsx\"><strong>Enlarged Audience Template<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use this template spreadsheet to contact wider networks of stakeholders and increase your audience numbers. The prospecting information contained in the template will help you plan an effective promotion strategy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-5df83f98-a6d6-4cbf-92b8-8acda536463f\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Promotion_Dissemination_Template_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.xlsx\"><strong>Promotion and Dissemination Template<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Use this template spreadsheet to report the promotion and dissemination activities carried out by project partners for each training event. It will help you measure the estimated outreach, and identify relevant target groups and channels.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<h3 class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color\"><strong>4. Assess impact<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-fc08716e-0bde-4c29-9c60-15388869386d\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/Post_Training_Survey_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.docx\"><strong>Survey &#8211; Feedback<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The methodology of this survey can be reproduced to collect attendees&#8217; feedback at the end of the training session. It will help you set KPIs and measure the relevance of the training sessions.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flex wp-container-11 wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\">\n<h3 class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#704893\"><strong>5. Report<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-bb17e4af-4026-4ed2-b16e-0be427289f7b\" href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/List_Past_Events_TRIPLE_Training_Toolkit.docx\"><strong>List &#8211; Past Events<\/strong><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The list of past events enables you to gather relevant information on each training event in a single file. It serves as an example which can be adapted to your training series to gain time when carrying out reporting activities.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-column\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/triple-logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3405\" width=\"139\" height=\"137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/triple-logo.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/triple-logo-300x295.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/triple-logo-768x756.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 139px) 100vw, 139px\" \/><\/figure><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><em>Additional information<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>What for? <\/strong>The purpose of the TRIPLE Training Toolkit is to provide effective support to the research community in the uptake and application of Open Science and FAIR Data management practices within training activities and to address the frequent findability and reusability issues related to the management of digital training materials. The Toolkit serves as a reference for those wishing to reproduce this experiment within their own institution or for their own training activities.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>How? <\/strong>The Toolkit includes a set of reproducible templates that trainers can reuse and adapt to their needs. The Toolkit and the reference documents are deposited in Zenodo (DOI: <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.5281\/zenodo.7309919\">10.5281\/zenodo.7309919<\/a>) but you can also download them directly from this page by clicking on the template file names above. <\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The TRIPLE Training Toolkit is an open workflow in five steps that trainers can reproduce and adapt to organise training events following a FAIR-by-design method. It was created following the delivery of the TRIPLE Open Science Training Series.&nbsp; This figure<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":0,"parent":42,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3355"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3355"}],"version-history":[{"count":25,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3355\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3410,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3355\/revisions\/3410"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/42"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3355"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}